        public TileOptions(int zoom)
        Initializes a new instance of the TileManager.TileOptions class.
        Parameters:
        zoom - Target zoom level. Some options (pen width, FRC level) will be set automatically based on the specified zoom level. If specified zoom not within allowed zoom level range, options will be set to default value (same as calling TileOptions .ctor without parameters).

      • setFrcLevel

        public TileManager.TileOptions setFrcLevel(int frcLevel)
        Sets the Federal Road Classification code level(s) for a tile. The default value is TileManager.TILE_FRC_LEVEL_ALL.
        Parameters:
        frcLevel - The Federal Road Classification code of the TMCs to return. Can be one or a combination of the following values:
        • TileManager.TILE_FRC_LEVEL_ALL
        • TileManager.TILE_FRC_LEVEL_1
        • TileManager.TILE_FRC_LEVEL_2
        • TileManager.TILE_FRC_LEVEL_3

        • TileManager.TILE_FRC_LEVEL_5
        • TileManager.TILE_FRC_LEVEL_6
        • TileManager.TILE_FRC_LEVEL_7
        Returns:
        This instance of the TileManager.TileOptions class.

      • setCoverage

        Parameters:

        Parameters:
